---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="From Surviving to Living: A Free Webinar for Parent Carers | OAKonsult"
	description="For many parent carers, life feels like survival. This free webinar is a roadmap to healing, clarity, and strength."
	path="/blog/from-surviving-to-living"
>
	<article>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="container" style="max-width: 780px;">
				<p class="section-kicker reveal">Blog &middot; February 20, 2026</p>
				<h1 class="reveal" style="--delay: 0.05s;">From Surviving to Living: A Free Webinar for Parent Carers</h1>
				<p class="muted-copy reveal" style="--delay: 0.08s;">
					For many parent carers, life still feels like survival. This webinar was created for you.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container" style="max-width: 780px;">
				<div class="reveal">
					<p style="color: var(--oak-muted); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
						Waking up tired. Carrying responsibilities that never pause. Putting yourself last,
						again and again. You love deeply. But somewhere along the way, you disappeared.
					</p>

					<p style="color: var(--oak-muted); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
						This webinar was created for that version of you &mdash; the one who is strong on
						the outside but exhausted inside.
					</p>

					<div class="callout callout--gold" style="margin: 1.5rem 0;">
						<h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem;">What You'll Learn</h2>
						<ul class="simple-list" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
							<li>Why burnout happens (and why it's not your fault)</li>
							<li>How to reconnect with yourself without guilt</li>
							<li>What it means to move from surviving to living</li>
							<li>How healing, clarity, and strength are still possible for you</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<p style="color: var(--oak-muted); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
						You didn't plan for this life. You planned to raise a child, not to become a carer
						overnight. And yet here you are. Still showing up. Still loving. Still holding everything
						together &mdash; often at the cost of yourself.
					</p>

					<p style="color: var(--oak-muted); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
						<strong>"From Surviving to Living"</strong> is not just a webinar. It's a pause. A breath.
						A reminder that you matter too.
					</p>

					<p style="color: var(--oak-muted); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
						Hosted by Mrs Olufunke Adeloye, alongside incredible voices who understand this
						journey deeply. This is an honest, gentle, and powerful conversation about healing,
						clarity, strength, and finding your way back to yourself as a parent carer.
					</p>

					<p style="color: var(--oak-muted); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
						Because you deserve more than survival. You deserve to live.
					</p>

					<div class="callout" style="margin: 1.5rem 0; text-align: center;">
						<h3>Free Webinar</h3>
						<p><strong>From Surviving to Living:</strong> A Parent Carer's Roadmap to Healing, Clarity &amp; Strength</p>
						<div class="callout-actions" style="justify-content: center;">
							<a class="button button-primary" href="/contact-us">Register Your Interest</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--oak-muted);">
						Someone you know may need this too &mdash; please share.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</article>
</Layout>
